The '''Half Transmogrified Junction''' is as it's name suggests, half of a [[en/Community/Junctionary/Transmogrified]] Junction.

[[File:en/Ttd.half.transmogrified.png|frame|none|Half Transmogrified Junction]]

===Pros===
*Quite fast.
*Quite compact.
*Traffic jams are unlikely since tracks split before they merge.
*No loops.

===Cons===
*There are double slopes on one of the straight tracks.
*Half of the paths through the junction have at least one slope.

